<monorepo_overview>

App Starter monorepo for building applications with shared packages and serverless infrastructure. All code is TypeScript. Managed with pnpm workspaces and Turborepo; deployed with SST to AWS.

</monorepo_overview>

<tech_stack>

- pnpm (workspaces)
- Turborepo (build/test/lint orchestration)
- SST on AWS (infrastructure + local dev shell)
- Supabase (Postgres)
- Prisma (ORM)
- Next.js (frontend)
- Node.js + TypeScript (backend and shared)

</tech_stack>

<repository_structure>

```text
/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/           # Next.js app (frontend)
│   ├── backend/       # Serverless backend (SST, Hono, tRPC, Prisma)
├── packages/
│   ├── config/        # Shared configuration + env
│   ├── eslint/        # Shared ESLint config
│   ├── tsconfig/      # Shared TypeScript configs
